Detailed Description

MGLCisect_vector defines linked list of MGLCisect.

Used to represent Intersection points of a loop and a curve.

void MGLCisect_vector::update_lepoint ( const MGLEPoint &  lep  ) 

Update MGLEPoint in this LCisect_vector.

This is to update MGLEPoints in this obtained before MGLoop::make_vertex and the loop is updated by MGLoop::make_vertex. Generally speaking, when make_vertex is invoked after MGLCisect_vector is obtaind, the MGLEPoints in the MGLCisect_vector do not contain correct values, since a new edge is inserted int the MGComplex's cell vector.
